articles.title: Ukraine Russia war updates: Missile strike kills 51 at café - USA TODAY
articles.description: As President Volodymyr Zelenskyy traveled to Spain to seek support from European leaders, his country was attacked by Russian drones and a missile.
articles.content: Russia blasted several Ukrainian provinces Thursday with a multi-pronged attack killing at least 51 civilians in a missile strike at a village café and market in the northeast and swarming south and … [+5960 chars]
